node.text:
What P&G trailblazer Kishore Karuppan is describing in this video is called “entrepreneur joy.” It is something he says he felt as he launched CuBe – an innovation that uses block chain technology to prevent coupon fraud. #PGInnovation 
 
Kishore and his team are disrupting a decades old industry – #couponing! CuBe has already saved companies like P&G billions of dollars. If you Google Kishore’s name you will find that CuBE is patent pending! #PGInnovation 
 
As the middle child out of 5 boys, Kishore says he always felt the need to prove himself. This mentality helped drive him to create CuBE despite many opportunities to give up. 
 
To learn more about CuBE and what it could mean for the future of coupons, click #linkibio. 
 
The Signal Trailblazers series features P&G, managers and executives around the globe who are innovating new ways to make business a force for good and a force for growth. #PGTrailblazers #PGSignal
